erpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">10\u003C/span>πεὶ ἐκ τᾶς ἰδίας ἐξεπέτο-\u003Cbr id=\"al11-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">11\u003C/span>μες καὶ ἐπλανώμεθα πα-\u003Cbr id=\"al12-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">12\u003C/span>ρακαλοῦντες καὶ δεκόμε-\u003Cbr id=\"al13-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">13\u003C/span>νοι καὶ πόλι καὶ χώραι ἔδο-\u003Cbr id=\"al14-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">14\u003C/span>ξε τᾶι βουλᾶι καὶ τᾶι ἁλίαι \u003Cbr id=\"al15-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">15\u003C/span>εἴμειν αὐτοῖς εὔνοιαν κ̣αὶ \u003Cbr id=\"al16-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">16\u003C/span>ἰσοπολιτείαν ποτὶ τὸν δᾶ-\u003Cbr id=\"al17-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">17\u003C/span>μον τῶν Ἐντελλίνων κα-\u003Cbr id=\"al18-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">18\u003C/span>τὰ παντὸς χρόνου τὸ δὲ ἁ-\u003Cbr id=\"al19-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">19\u003C/span>λίασμα τοῦτο οἱ ἄρχοντες \u003Cbr id=\"al20-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">20\u003C/span>ἐς χάλκωμα γράψαντες \u003Cbr id=\"al21-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">21\u003C/span>ἀναθέντων ἐς τὸ βου-\u003Cbr id=\"al22-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">22\u003C/span>λευτήριον \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.10)\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"author":3,"date":4,"citedRange":126,"ptr":127,"title":2,"citation":5},"308",{"target":128},"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/LAKV5V4S"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
